    <string name="tooltip_tuning_system">Tuning system:\n\n12 Swars (JI ratios): Standard swars with komal and teevra Ma variants.\nS, r, R, g, m, M, P, d, D, n, N\nRecommended for general practice.\n\n22-Shruti: Shrutis with microtonal variations (ati-komal, komal, teevra &amp; ati-teevra Ma).\nS, r1, r2, R1, R2, g1, g2, G1, G2, m1, m2, M1, M2, P, d1, d2, D1, D2, n1, n2, N1, N2\nRecommended for accuracy with raag riyaaz.</string>
